Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:26.26,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}I wake once again to a sleepy morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.90,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}And carefully fasten my necktie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:39.37,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,210)}As I pass the door to the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:46.25,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,0)}I walk with my chest held just a little high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:53.38,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}The wind blows through the days spent just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:56.84,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I heard it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:02.85,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I felt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:06.73,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,It now trembles within my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:10.11,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,190)}I felt it would happen soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:18.20,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,120)}I watched the millions of stars as they disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:24.71,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,And waved them goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:29.79,Opening-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}So happy for them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's out partying late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you must be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:02.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:04.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi isn't harmless anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:07.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... that's not Kanade at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:09.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we weren't resisting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:12.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade never turned her sword against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!  What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, surround her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:24.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What are you giving orders for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:26.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:22.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrated fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't have distortion on, we can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!  Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kanade alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a really deep wound, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a fatal wound will heal automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:03.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can there be two of the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this world really become that crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:12.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when we infiltrated Tenshi-area?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had software on her computer that would develop "skills", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one on there that we'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have used that skill.  Harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Harmonics?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of power is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking at the screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a skill that splits one's body into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:35.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A doppelgänger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:36.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:41.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a skill that Tenshi herself created using software, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure didn't seem like she was in control anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing was different than her.  More warlike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade only uses her powers to protect herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the swords were used that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just used to deflect our bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:58.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.  You're a pretty incompetent group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san being the exception, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's composed of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason her other self sprang forth is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she wanted to call forth a powerful attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From back then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still just following the order of the main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade has never wanted to attack before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you sure are sticking up for her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's our current problem then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it how we're gonna fight Tenshi's clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:43.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?  It's how we're gonna {\i1}erase{\i0} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if she created it on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:46.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:47.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there must be a way to erase it on purpose, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:53.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just wait until she wakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:58.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she summoned it on purpose, would it really do {\i1}this{\i0} to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, she summoned it unconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she was unable to erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they had to extinguish each other, that's all she could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing isn't gonna disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be hanging around this world from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we're being allowed to remain at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But starting tomorrow, we probably won't be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we start to act outside the boundaries of "exemplary behavior"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll quickly turn into a blood-stained battle just like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she's not even the Student Council President anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:30.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her desire to correct our behavior is still absolutely present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only now she's enforcing it in a more warlike manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:32.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the worst possible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even have enough time to organize our resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you buy me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How shall we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:46.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to class, and pretend to pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't actually concentrate on the teacher, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really take the classes seriously, you'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:53.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be discovered by Tenshi's clone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So just immerse yourself in your own separate activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And separately, try to hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May nobody disappear.  I pray we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I already {\i1}know{\i0} that she splits into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know how to make it disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Player?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the software manual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.  It's all in English!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even under normal circumstances, I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  It popped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this its range?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!  This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:39.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this order is given, it should disappear on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:41.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, what are the conditions, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.  I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just bust the computer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:51.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't make it disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  I'll just write it into the program I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait time, 10 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's {\i1}that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting 10 seconds is kinda long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I do it under 10 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.  It looks like that worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the clone create this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I delete it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I've been pretty careful so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to keep my editing to a minimum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just need her to use Harmonics again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:47.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Absorb will start up, and her clone should go back to her main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she went out someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She promised to stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She promised that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:08.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by this destruction, it looks like she was abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You!  What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"You?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wrote something into the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that girl uses her power again, a supplemental power will be invoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the clone should return to her main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was mostly guessing, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the enemy moved faster than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she hides her main body, we can't destroy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While avoiding the notice of that monstrous Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could have gotten away with just faking it in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How well can you pull off a diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?  A diversion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you join GirlDeMo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I looked up to Iwasawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,GirlDeMo is supposed to be a diversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.  I can't just {\i1}distract{\i0} someone that scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your Senpai!  I should be getting mad here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um.  I might pee my pants during the concert, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your determination but, we might not need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a directive for all members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather information on Tenshi's whereabouts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.34,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yo! Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.41,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moonwalk!  It's a moonwalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.42,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the information gathered on short notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a high probability that she's being confined in the Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it would have to be the newer one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one we blew up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:30.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And very far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going down there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time we were all nearly wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  Are you guys scared or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, {\i1}you{\i0} were the first to die last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For everyone's sakes, I'll keep singing, even if I start to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:50.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how brave I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Using a diversionary tactic against that thing won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:58.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?  No distraction this time.  We're gonna do this openly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While fighting Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we clear?  The operation is to descend to the destroyed Guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and safely recover the original Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation... start!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like last time's traps haven't been reset.  Lucky~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:32.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...if Tenshi shows up I think I'm gonna pee my pants either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}should{\i0} care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}should{\i0} care!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She appeared already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got handguns!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This might go faster than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:16.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's another clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there another?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, the enemies are multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a big deal, but man, he was done in right off the bat again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.  Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about the one behind us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get the enemy right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You all seem pretty busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe, we're gonna run out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make us an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:49.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 more seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't make it you'll be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:01.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:03.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:06.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:08.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:10.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's two of that ferocious Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:20.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is even worse than the last time we came down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there two now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The clones can use Hand Sonic and Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's no surprise they can use Harmonics as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you certainly are a feeble-minded bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san being the exception, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I explain the problem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's two problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is how many clones have been created?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If clones can make clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no limit to how many there may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not just two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be ten or twenty or more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri appended that ability, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The clones should be returning to the main body?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just wait for them to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the second problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if she'd already made a number of copies before the ability was appended?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.  Peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Otonashi-san is a sublime nobleman, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it knew that we were going to be coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and began to mass-produce clones...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and stationed them around the Guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:31.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean this is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.00,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's already two behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools have no chance of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there could be swarms of them that await us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't resupply our weapons, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is wait for them to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What could their goal possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it must be to make us completely obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's her mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that we'll just silently disappear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:04.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good plan for taking us out in one clean sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 3, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsushita-godan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:41.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go while I'm still conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to sound like the hero on the brink of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go while we still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it, Matsushita-godan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up... to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:54.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not waste Matsushita-kun's sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him we understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the first move is the best way to deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:09.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi's body is tiny, so it's best to restrict her movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how ridiculously strong she might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a judo hold should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:18.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Judo lessons Matsushita-kun gave us should come in handy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we can sacrifice one of ourselves for each clone we encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can save the original...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then we can save those who sacrifice themselves as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.74,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.42,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Get chance and luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:49.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this scenario looking like the end of a shounen manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.  We're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This body of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to show it to you has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.  Like this would scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How fooliiiiiiish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:22.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there in that dark corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:27.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lonely little girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.  Oh no, he's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-san, that's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out. I just misspoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go next, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... somebody say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:50.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I don't know his name though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many does this make now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even counting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:03.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hang on until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:08.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this feeling she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you've gotta keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if by some chance{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going, then go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love him or hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The explosion site of the Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all gonna go to the bottom at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi-kun and Yui will look for the original Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find her, get her to use Harmonics immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better for me to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:46.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you listen to Hinata-kun?  That girl is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then I'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too puny, it's not even worth considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super-strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this will turn out to be our final operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.  Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:07.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Where's Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda felt like I heard a really short scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she fall prey to Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, we're the only ones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the last one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just stand there, go find the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:37.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Howling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are plugged, so I can't really hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:51.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want, I'll use my other knife to slit your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:20:58.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:13.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from the SSS put their lives on the line to come save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to push you like this, but I need you to use an ability for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:22.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use that, it'll help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use it, will your body be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Harmonics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you changed the program, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  You'll all return to her body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All those cold-hearted copies of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:53.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even clones have consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be assimilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:22:02.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the copies that attacked you will return to this one's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:05.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For her to take all that consciousness in at one time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:40.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade!
