Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:53.43,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(380,300)}I've always walked alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:00.90,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,340)}When I turned around, everyone was far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:08.57,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Even so, I walked on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:14.22,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(230,400)}That's what it was to be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:22.27,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(330,380)}I'm not afraid of anything anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:30.50,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,540)}That's what I try to tell myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:41.77,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(540,0)}Eventually, everyone will be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:49.42,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:57.22,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:24:04.39,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,640)}I will fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:12.22,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,780)}I will never show you my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:18.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c290] What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c12] This is the first time Tenshi has ever been in that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:20.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c28] But we can only withstand that for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:21.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c23] There's about a 1% chance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c276] You want to help me strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:21.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c93] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:22.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c147] Somebody hit that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c83] We're going to help. Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:24.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c143] Nobody's gonna help anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c239] Am I gonna disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:25.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c34] Who is God supporting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:24.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c160] Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.73,0:24:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c209] Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,[c221] I... remember everything.
